allocPSA Installation
=====================

Please note: If you are upgrading, please read the file called UPGRADING.

allocPSA is generally intended to run with PHP>=5 and MySQL>=4 on a Linux
server. It may also run on a Windows box, but possibly not with the full
functionality.

To install allocPSA:

1) Put the allocPSA source code in a directory called eg "alloc" in your
   webservers document root.

2) Open that URL with your web browser eg: http://webserver/alloc/
   and complete the installation.


Please feel free to contact us at Cyber IT Solutions <info@cyber.com.au> or use
the forums at http://sourceforge.net/projects/allocpsa/ if you have any
questions.

Contact support@allocpsa.com for commercial and hosting enquiries.

